classes:

Book - ISBN, Author, Title. getters
BookRecord - Book*, numOfCopies, borrowers & waiting list. IsAvailable, NextBorrower(?), Borrow, Return, Report
BooksAdmin - list of BookRecord*. add/remove/search. Borrow, Return

Person - ID, name, phone. getters.      // could be part of BorrowerRecord
BorrowerRecord - Person*, list. Borrow, Return, Report
BorrowerAdmin - list of BorrowerRecord. add/remove/search. Borrow, Return, ReportOfAll

Library - lists of BorrowerRecord & BookRecord, 
